reviewText: Don't get me wrong, I love this series but I felt that not enough detail were there for me when I bought this product; I thought I was buying volume 2 of 6 not volume's 3 and 4 in a combo package. And I already had the previously mentioned volumes so it was kinda a waste of money for me.
cd box is in fine condition. No art is inside. The cds are in perfect condition so no real complaints.
I love s-cry-ed, always have.  The dvd was shipped quickly and the dvd was in great condition.  I'm very happy.
